ess: \"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">service</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mailupdater</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Service</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"n\">service</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Vacation pix\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">as</span> <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"See attachments.\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">attach</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"file.txt\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">attach</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"image.png\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"These are my vacation pictures.\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"n\">service</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Reminder\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">as</span> <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Did you see the previous email I sent?\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Two new emails will appear in your inbox.</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Sending emails to multiple recipients is easy:</p>\n<pre>